snippet.title: Longplay of Ben 10: Omniverse 2
snippet.description:
Longplay of Ben 10: Omniverse 2, played as the NTSC version on the Wii. This game's version was released on Nov. 5th, 2013. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

0:00:00 - Start
0:01:10 - Learning the Ropes
0:04:55 - Stow Away
0:23:47 - Mess Hall Mashup
0:37:29 - Welcome to Erf
1:01:05 - Undertown and Beyond
1:17:48 - The Core of the Problem
1:36:48 - No Time for Sightseeing
1:53:11 - Trouble with Way Bad
2:00:18 - Credits
